metadata.name: SOULWAVE - Colors Of My Mind
metadata.description:
The Soulwave is the initial feeling, that wave of energy for a new idea or urge to do something new.  
*  
The Collection, COLORS OF MY MIND, represents the freedom to do what u feel without a doubt, in the exact moment u feel it. Made 4 the soul.  
*  
Handpainted on Procreate by Samora 'Oibel1.' Bazarrabusa in January 2022. All rights reserved.
